room_title: Escape room "The Game Master" by CluedIn Escape Rooms in Chicago
room_description: The Game Master has kidnapped the mayor! You’ll have to use your wits to solve his board game and video game puzzles and traps. The Game Master plays by his own rules, so you won’t need to know anything about the games to solve them. You only have an hour to do it though! Will it be game over for the mayor, or can your team save him in time?
